          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0394P0_20021119_CWS_6' title='Link to this speech by Mr Andrew Smith' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-andrew-smith" title="Mr Andrew Smith">The Secretary of State for Work and Pensions (Mr. Andrew Smith)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">The new rates of benefits proposed from April 2003 are set out in the tables. The Annual uprating of benefits will take place in the first full week of the tax year. In 2003, this will be the week beginning 7 April. My right hon. Friend the Secretary of State for Northern Ireland proposes to introduce similar changes for Northern Ireland.</p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_17ws' title='Col. 17WS &mdash; HC Deb 19 November 2002 vol 394 c17WS' name='column_17ws' href='#column_17ws' rel='bookmark'>17WS</a><p><table>
